org.postnote.entity

Class PostNote

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.postnote.entity.PostNote
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity(name="POST_NOTE")
public class PostNote
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a single note.

    As JPA Entity it belong to the POST_NOTE table using id as primary (generated) key. None of the field is nullable.

    Processed by JAXB, generate an XML document using postnote as root node.

    Since:
    2014-06-12
    Version:
